   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2428, recto: (1) I, Tagape, daughter of Pmai, (2) who lives in Roma (3) in(?) Jeme, writes to Manasseh, son of Pegosh, (4) who lives in Jeme, (5) district of Ermont, in (6) the same nome.  I owe (7) you one artaba of wheat (8) and one ment to the artaba, and (9) one oipe of sesame, and (10)...maje as interest.  These (11) I am prepared to give (12) you in the coming Paone...(13) son of Jacob, (14) [wrote this] sherd on (15) the...of Epep (16) ...son of Pbelle, (17) [I am] witness.  (18) Samuel (19) ...I am witness...</ab>
         </div>
